{
	"folder": "NfxMJJFyraG9EXbD",
	"name": "Lapidate (Air Savant)",
	"type": "spell",
	"img": "icons/weapons/thrown/bolas-stone.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You pick up an object or a small creature. You shake it, saying a few words to animate it, and then throw it at your target. Your magic aids your aim and allows you to strike with unnatural force.</em></p><p><strong>Ranged Spell Attack</strong></p><p>You pick up a small object or a creature you are &amp;reference[grappled]{grappling} which is at least two sizes smaller than you. You throw it at a creature or location up to 60 ft. away.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]] damage* and the thrown object or creature takes the same damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Miss:</strong> Thrown object or creatures takes [[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]] damage*.</p><p></p></li></ul><p><strong>*Using Higher Level Spell Slots:</strong> This spell's damage increases by [[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]]{1d10} when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d10 bludgeoning]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d10 bludgeoning]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d10 bludgeoning]]).</p><p></p><p><em>An object or creature thrown by this spell does not take damage from falling, as the spell magically throttles the speed to the same speed constantly. If a creature is thrown 60 ft. into the air and then falls, they take this spell's damage when they hit the ground and no falling damage.</em></p>",
			"chat": "<p><strong>Ranged Spell Attack</strong></p><p>You pick up a small object or a creature you are &amp;reference[grappled]{grappling} which is at least two sizes smaller than you. You throw it at a creature or location up to 60 ft. away.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]] damage* and the thrown object or creature takes the same damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Miss:</strong> Thrown object or creatures takes [[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]] damage*.</p><p></p></li></ul><p><strong>*Using Higher Level Spell Slots:</strong> This spell's damage increases by [[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]]{1d10} when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d10 bludgeoning]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d10 bludgeoning]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d10 bludgeoning]]).</p><p></p>"
		},
